These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: mirinda, iced-tea, milk, tea
Sport: baseball, rugby, handball, parkour
1. Beverage:mirinda is on the right of Sport:handball##1
2. Sport:parkour is on the far left##1
3. Sport:handball is between Sport:rugby and Beverage:iced-tea##2
4. Beverage:tea is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:milk is between Beverage:iced-tea and Beverage:mirinda##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | tea         | iced-tea   | milk | mirinda       |
| Sport      | parkour | baseball | handball   | rugby |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: baking, skydiving, board-games, rock-climbing
Nationality: indonesian, mexican, thai, indian
1. Nationality:indian is between Hobby:board-games and Nationality:mexican##2
2. Hobby:rock-climbing is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:thai is on the right of Nationality:indonesian##1
4. Hobby:baking is on the left of Nationality:indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | baking | board-games | rock-climbing |
| Nationality   | mexican    | indian   | indonesian | thai       |

