.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
Food: apple, plum, eggplant, potato
Nationality: mexican, argentine, nigerian, italian
1. Nationality:nigerian is on the right of Food:potato##1
2. Nationality:nigerian is between Nationality:argentine and Food:plum##2
3. Nationality:argentine is on the far left##1
4. Nationality:italian is on the left of Food:eggplant##1
5. Food:plum == Nationality:italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | potato    | apple | plum   | eggplant  |
| Nationality   | argentine | nigerian   | italian | mexican |

