.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
Pet: rabbit, ferret, turtle, chinchilla
Sport: parkour, cycling, weightlifting, water-polo
1. Sport:cycling == Pet:ferret##1
2. Pet:rabbit is between Sport:parkour and Pet:chinchilla##2
3. Sport:cycling is on the far right##1
4. Pet:rabbit is on the right of Sport:weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet     | chinchilla   | rabbit    | turtle       | ferret   |
| Sport   | weightlifting | water-polo | parkour | cycling |

